Ingredient: ripe avocados - halved, pitted, and peeled
agave nectar, or more to taste
sugar-free pumpkin spice coffee creamer (such as International Delight®)

apple pie spice or ground cinnamon
vanilla bean, slit lengthwise, seeds scraped
